4.0,What was BCP's Return on Equity (ROE) in Q1 2019?,BCP's Return on Equity (ROE) in Q1 2019 was 6.151%.,SELECT (total_revenue_quarter - total_expenses_quarter) / shareholder_equity AS ROE FROM financialmetrics fm INNER JOIN period p ON fm.period_id = p.id WHERE fm.company_id = (SELECT id FROM company WHERE symbol = 'BCP') AND p.year = 2019 AND p.quarter = 1 LIMIT 1
